What a wonderful twist in this story of the one called Sandra.  Shrouded in mystery, she captivated onlookers around the world with a phenomenal photogenic presence.  Fans watched as she came of age, maturing into the model that all others have to be judged by.  Then, with imaginations running wild over what her future sets would look like, she fell in love, started a family and quit modeling.  
Yes Fame-Girls has plenty of sets from Sandra, yet to be released, but for now, she is done modeling.  Making purchases from her official sites (whenever you are able) is the best way to thank her for the many hours of hard work she has put in over the last decade.
There will never be another like her.
